data.description: Welcome to 969 Parsons in the charming neighborhood of Ashview Heights! This stunning modern farmhouse, completed in 2022, offers a perfect blend of contemporary luxury and timeless elegance. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and a plethora of upgrades, this home is sure to exceed your expectations. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by soaring 10+ foot ceilings on the main level, enhancing the spacious and airy ambiance throughout. The open concept floor plan seamlessly integrates the family room, dining area, and kitchen, creating the ideal space for both relaxing and entertaining. Cozy around the electric fireplace with custom built-in shelving on each side, or dine in the large dining area and kitchen. Prepare to be amazed by the chef's kitchen, which features a large center island perfect for gatherings. Equipped with top-of-the-line Samsung appliances, including a smart 4-door fridge/freezer with a built-in beverage center, a three-rack Samsung dishwasher, a Cosmo 36-inch dual fuel range and commercial stove, and a built-in Frigidaire microwave, this kitchen is truly a culinary paradise and plenty of storage in the walk-in pantry. The private, large, and luxurious primary suite boasts a spa like ensuite bath with his and her vanity, large custom tile shower, and walk in closet. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms upstairs provide ample space for family and guests not to mention the stylish custom tiled secondary bath. Other notable upgrades (but not all) include energy efficient custom windows and blinds throughout, under stairs kids hang out / reading nook w/ rotating tv mount included, custom Container Store shelving and drawers in butler's pantry and all closets, like new Samsung washer and dryer, SimpliSafe security system with window and entry door motion sensors, Blink front and back doorbell and exterior cameras, Control 4 entertainment with surround sound/speakers, deep attached one car garage with storage and mudroom, corner lot w/ large private driveway with white vinyl and Black Spearhead Steel iron rod fencing surround the perimeter of the home w/ a front gate and private front porch and back porch. And more - ask your agent for the full upgrade list. Located in the sought-after Ashview Heights neighborhood, this home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and urban convenience. With its close proximity to the Beltline, parks, restaurants, shopping, and major highways, you'll have everything you need right at your fingertips. Schedule your showing today and prepare to fall in love with this show-stopping home.
